1. Frontend
Key Features:
User-friendly interface for uploading book images or PDFs.
Real-time display of extracted text for review and editing.
Responsive design optimized for desktop and mobile use.




2. Backend
Technology Used: Django




3. OCR Engine
Technology Used: PaddleOCR




4. AI Integration
Technology Used: Azure Cognitive Services & Gemini API




5. Cloud Services
Technology Used: Azure Cloud



Description : 
             A comprehensive web-based Optical Character Recognition (OCR) system for extracting and processing text from books, built using PaddleOCR, Azure Cognitive Services, Gemini API, and Django.
